          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Cross section values for neutron capture in Ni-58 and",
                " Ni-60, where the primary gamma rays go to levels of",
                " Ni-59 and Ni-61 in the excitation energy ranges",
                " 0.9-2.0 MeV and 0.0-0.9 MeV, respectively. It is not",
                " possible to conclude that the second peak in the gamma",
                " spectra is due entirely to capture in Ni-60, since",
                " capture leading to levels around 1.5 MeV in Ni-59 may",
                " contribute.  For this reason no abundance correction",
                " has been applied to the experimental values."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Natural nickel in the form of 15 cm diam.,",
                "1.5 cm thick disks."
